| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4857 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5d20ff5f-d986-5dbf-91b7-103e169dc47a"
